aia (pteridófita).jpg|100px]] |- | | ''[[Protoischnurus|Protoischnurus axelrodorum]]'' | 105 Ma | Early Cretaceous | Crato Formation | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale023.html ''Protoischnurus axelrodorum'']</ref> |- | | ''[[Araripemys|Araripemys barretoi]]'' | 110 Ma | Early Cretaceous | Santana Formation | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale032.html ''Araripemys barretoi'']</ref> |- | | ''[[Bauruemys|Bauruemys elegans]]'' | 80 Ma | Late Cretaceous | [[Presidente Prudente Formation]] | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale018.html ''Bauruemys elegans'']</ref> |- | | ''[[Beurlenia|Beurlenia araripensis]]'' | 105 Ma | Early Cretaceous | Crato Formation | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale031.html ''Beurlenia araripensis'']</ref> |- | | ''[[Araripichthys|Araripichthys castilhoi]]'' | 105-110 Ma | Early Cretaceous | Crato & Santana Formations | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale030.html ''Araripichthys castilhoi'']</ref> |- | | ''[[Stereosternum]]'' | 275 Ma | [[Permian]] | [[Irati Formation]] | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale020.html ''Stereosternum'']</ref> |- | | Lizard | 105 Ma | Early Cretaceous | Crato Formation | align=center | <ref>[http://www.museunacional.ufrj.br/dir/exposicoes/paleontologia/pale008.html Lizard]</ref> |- |}
